# Luna OS — gaming package list
# config/package-lists/gaming.list.chroot
#
# Lutris is included and presented to the user under its real name and
# real branding — no rebranding/disguising of third-party software.
# Lutris itself only launches games the user has legitimate access to;
# Luna OS does not bundle or fake any purchase/account flow.

## Game launcher (real Lutris, real branding)
lutris

## Performance daemons
gamemode
mangohud

## Retro emulation (RetroArch + libretro cores)
retroarch
libretro-core-info
retroarch-assets
libretro-nestopia
libretro-snes9x
libretro-mednafen-psx
libretro-mgba
libretro-fbneo
libretro-genesis-plus-gx
libretro-mupen64plus-next

## Windows compatibility layer (minimal Wine — not full Proton GE)
wine64
wine32:i386
winetricks

## Controller support
xpad-dkms
joystick
jstest-gtk

## Memory management
zram-tools
